tasks.task_query: Create a new design file
Rename the file to FigmaCrashCourse
Rename Page 1 to Mobile
Add a new page named Components

images.instruction: Click plus icon in left sidebar;

tasks.task_query: Show rulers in the canvas
Create an iPhone 14 frame and name it Mobile/Home

images.instruction: Click layer name in left panel;

tasks.task_query: Add a 4‑column layout grid with 16 margin and 16 gutter

images.instruction: In right sidebar click Layout grid + icon;

tasks.task_query: Set Mobile/Home frame fill to #FFFFFF

images.instruction: In right sidebar click Fill color;

tasks.task_query: Place Images/hero.jpg inside Mobile/Home
Insert a text title and set size to 32

images.instruction: Click in center of Mobile/Home frame;

tasks.task_query: Place Icons/search.svg at the top of Mobile/Home
Set search icon constraints to Right and Top

images.instruction: Select the search icon in the middle;
In right sidebar select Horizontal Constraints

tasks.task_query: Create a Desktop 1440 frame named Web/Home

images.instruction: In right sidebar click Desktop with 1440 resolution;
Click layer name in left panel;

tasks.task_query: Place Logos/brandA.svg at top left of Web/Home

images.instruction: Click inside Web/Home near top left

tasks.task_query: Add a 12‑column grid with 80 margin and 24 gutter to Web/Home

images.instruction: In right sidebar click Layout grid + button;

tasks.task_query: Insert headline text and set size to 48
Set headline fill color to #3366CC

images.instruction: In right sidebar click Fill color;

tasks.task_query: Create color style Brand/Primary from headline fill

images.instruction: With headline selected click Color style icon;

tasks.task_query: Insert text Buy now inside Mobile/Home
Place a Button/Primary instance on Mobile/Home using Assets

images.instruction: Click Assets tab in left sidebar;

tasks.task_query: Export Button/Primary as PNG 2× to Exports/button_primary.png
Place Avatars/avatar1.png on Mobile/Home

images.instruction: Click inside Mobile/Home below blue icon

tasks.task_query: Round avatar corners to 64
Add a 2 px white stroke to avatar
Add a drop shadow effect to Button/Primary
Create a Mobile/Details frame (iPhone 14)

images.instruction: In right sidebar click iPhone 14 plus;
Click layer name in left panel;

tasks.task_query: Prototype: On click of Button/Primary instance navigate to Mobile/Details

images.instruction: Click Prototype tab in right sidebar;

tasks.task_query: Export Web/Home frame as PDF to Exports/web_home.pdf
